data.name: dstJournalEntry.CommandText
data.value: SELECT j.TransactionNo, a.Name AS Account, s.Name AS Subsidiary, jd.Debit, jd.Credit, jd.Remarks FROM tblJournals j INNER JOIN tblJournalDetails jd ON jd.JournalId = j.Id INNER JOIN tblAccounts a ON a.Id = jd.AccountId LEFT OUTER JOIN tblSubsidiaries s ON s.Id = jd.SubsidiaryId WHERE j.Id = @Id

data.name: dstDetail.CommandText
data.value: SELECT Id, BillId, ItemId, AccountId, SubsidiaryId, Amount, VATTypeId, VATRate, VATAmount, GrossAmount, ATCId, WithholdingTax, DiscountAmount, Total, Remarks FROM tblBillDetails WHERE BillId = @Id

data.name: $this.CommandText
data.value: SELECT Id, CompanyId, TransactionNo, [Date], ReferenceNo, ReferenceNo2, SubsidiaryId, GrossAmount, WithholdingTax, VATAmount, DiscountAmount, NetAmount, PaidAmount, Remarks, JournalId, Posted, Voided, VoidedById, DateVoided, CreatedById, DateCreated, ModifiedById, DateModified FROM tblBills WHERE Id = @Id
